==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Faller
<hw>Fall"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who,
or that which, falls.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Mach.)</fld> <def>A part which acts by falling, as
a stamp in a fulling mill, or the device in a spinning machine to arrest
motion when a thread breaks.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fallfish</ent>⟦br⟧
